@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_svmpbp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(0.65)
    v2 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.89 * tmp + 0.69)) * (wp.cos(v1 + 0.25) / (v2 + 0.76 / v0 + 0.79)))
    v2 = wp.exp(0.92)
    v1 = 0.51
    v0 = v2
    v1 = 0.21
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.exp(tmp + 0.89) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.01)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.57)) + v2)
    data[tid] = v0
